WEBVTT

00:07:57.138 --> 00:08:01.380
"OK, well, that sounds bad,
but that doesn't really affect me,

00:08:01.404 --> 00:08:03.580
because I'm a legal citizen.

00:08:03.604 --> 00:08:06.327
Why should I worry?
Because I have nothing to hide."

00:08:08.113 --> 00:08:10.560
And this is an argument
which doesn't make sense.

00:08:11.977 --> 00:08:14.786
Privacy is implied.

00:08:14.810 --> 00:08:18.475
Privacy is not up for discussion.

00:08:19.278 --> 00:08:21.150
This is not a question

00:08:21.174 --> 00:08:25.723
between privacy

00:08:25.747 --> 00:08:27.437
against security.

00:08:28.469 --> 00:08:32.024
It's a question of freedom